## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **ruxolitinib Jakafi 2019/2021** = first FDA SR-aGvHD (REACH-1, REACH-2) + first FDA SR-cGvHD (REACH-3). JAK1/2 small molecule paradigm shift in steroid-refractory GvHD. quantum-VQE 의 JAK kinase pocket 직접 fit.
2. **axatilimab Niktimvo 2024** = first FDA CSF-1R for cGvHD (Syndax + Incyte AGAVE-201). macrophage polarization (M1→M2 inhibition) + monocyte-macrophage axis 가 fibrotic cGvHD core. quantum-VQE 의 CSF-1R receptor pocket leverage.
3. **belumosudil Rezurock 2021** = ROCK2 selective inhibitor cGvHD ROCKstar trial. Th17/Treg balance 회복 + fibrotic cGvHD targeted. quantum-VQE 의 ROCK1 vs ROCK2 selectivity.
4. **ibrutinib Imbruvica 2017** = first FDA SR-cGvHD (BTK inhibitor 적응증 확대). B-cell + macrophage dual role. CLL → cGvHD pocket reuse.
5. **remestemcel-L Ryoncil 2024** = first FDA MSC pediatric SR-aGvHD (Mesoblast). cell therapy paradigm — small-molecule 한계 외. cross-regenerative + cell_therapy_platform.
6. **defibrotide Defitelio 2016** = first FDA VOD/SOS post-HSCT. endothelial protective + fibrinolytic. polydeoxyribonucleotide oligonucleotide mixture — quantum-VQE 의 oligonucleotide modeling 한정.
7. **letermovir Prevymis 2017 + maribavir Livtencity 2021** = CMV prophylaxis + refractory CMV post-HSCT (cross-infectious). terminase complex + pUL97 kinase 가 antiviral 신규 mechanism.
8. **post-Cy (PT-Cy) haploidentical paradigm** = Baltimore + Hopkins paradigm. cyclophosphamide post-transplant 가 alloreactive T-cell selective deletion. donor pool 확대 = matched 못 찾는 환자 구제.
9. **한국 K-HSCT + KSBMT + 가톨릭대/서울대/삼성서울/아산** = 다년 결과 누적. 한국 KCBMT + 식약처 cell therapy framework (cross-K_pharma_industry). 단일 mismatch + ATG + ECP + ruxolitinib paradigm 변화 (2017-2024).
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, HSCT + GvHD 임상 의미 한정.

